      <title>南非计划管理84亿美元的州财产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-plans-firm-to-manage-8-4-billion-of-state-property</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非公共工程部长40岁的迪恩·麦克弗森（Dean Macpherson）表示，他计划创建一家国有公司，该公司将管理政府的房地产投资组合，并诱使私人投资对基础设施项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-plans-firm-to-manage-8-4-billion-of-state-property</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 14:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼发誓要复兴加拿大战时时代的房屋建筑策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/carney-vows-to-revive-canada-s-wartime-era-homebuilding-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由派领导人马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）承诺，他的政府将通过一项计划以自第二次世界大战以来最雄心勃勃的计划来重新从事房屋建设业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/carney-vows-to-revive-canada-s-wartime-era-homebuilding-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:54:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普在华尔街播下经济恐惧时，美国股票昏昏欲睡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票市场的溃败周一加剧，担心唐纳德·特朗普总统的下一次关税推出会对全球经济产生震惊，而经济衰退的问题不断增加，这使得S＆amp; P 500指数在其最糟糕的季度与1980年代以来的其他地区相比，其最糟糕的季度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守派加拿大加拿大的“能源走廊”以结束美国的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/conservatives-pitch-canada-energy-corridor-to-end-us-reliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守派领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）誓言要批准快速批准，要求基础设施在国内和国外运输加拿大能源，而无需穿越美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/conservatives-pitch-canada-energy-corridor-to-end-us-reliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥地利认为欧盟的预算谴责不可避免为螺旋螺旋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/austria-sees-eu-budget-reprimand-unavoidable-as-deficit-spirals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长马库斯·马特鲍尔（Markus Marterbauer）表示，由于去年的经济发展比担心，奥地利将无法避免受到欧盟的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/austria-sees-eu-budget-reprimand-unavoidable-as-deficit-spirals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 12:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞在挪用公司裁定后提起法国选举禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-barred-from-2027-presidency-run-after-court-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼领导人海军的总统野心在法国法院被判犯有挪用公款罪名成立，并禁止在2027年的下一次大选中竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-barred-from-2027-presidency-run-after-court-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:50:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
